726146f-a.title: Queens: Beach 20th Street - New Haven Avenue
726146f-a.text:
Beach 20th, at the N.E. corner of New Eaven Ave., showing St. Mary's
Queen of the Sea (Roman Catholic) Church; Rev. 2immer was the pastor at
one time.
May 1923.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
